      <title>英国向基辅投下更多风暴阴影，斯塔默承诺提供支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/uk-sends-kyiv-more-storm-shadows-as-starmer-pledges-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国政府最近向乌克兰提供了数十枚“风暴阴影”巡航导弹，这是英国首相基尔·斯塔默上任以来首次向乌克兰提供该导弹。基尔·斯塔默已承诺将继续支持乌克兰对俄罗斯的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/uk-sends-kyiv-more-storm-shadows-as-starmer-pledges-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列和真主党即将达成协议 但袭击仍在继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/israel-and-hezbollah-on-the-cusp-of-deal-as-attacks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官员和知情人士透露，尽管双方仍在继续互相发射炮弹和火箭弹，但以色列和真主党已接近签署停火协议，该协议可能在未来几天内达成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/israel-and-hezbollah-on-the-cusp-of-deal-as-attacks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:10:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ken Leech 因交易分配计划遭检察官指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/ken-leech-sued-by-sec-over-alleged-cherry-picking-scheme</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西方资产管理公司 (Western Asset Management Co.) 前联席首席投资官肯·利奇 (Ken Leech) 被美国当局指控参与了所谓的“挑选”计划，即不公平地将表现较好的交易分配给优先投资组合，而将表现较差的交易分配给其他投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/ken-leech-sued-by-sec-over-alleged-cherry-picking-scheme</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 21:53:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
